snippet.textDisplay:
The lyrics are so grounded. It  brings out the poetry naturally through the song right from the first verse. Kudos Sajjad Ali. 
@CokeStudio this season was quite different from previous ones. Loads of new experiments and new voices in the studio Hina Nasrullah, Aima Baig. (Sorry for being a feminist here but they literally rocked).
House band rocks as always!!
A big thank you for a decade old Coke Studio which is an inspiration for  music experimentation the way you guys do it. Many more years to come!!
Last but not the least.. A big thanks to Rohail Hyatt for bringing this musical book in front of us. 
Love from Bharat!! 🤝

snippet.textDisplay:
Superbly melodious!! It's simple words and light composition extend the reach of this hamd to the masses. Brought tears to my eyes as I listened to it thinking of the almighty!! 
"Likhi hui baaton se bhi aati hai awaaz....." If only we human beings listen to the message of spreading love and kindness written in our scriptures!
Universal philosophy of goodness transcends religions and man made boundaries! Thanks to all the artists for soothing our souls.....Hope and pray Coke studio continues this good work in future!!!
